parameters: The Greatland Kingdom has a unit of wizards...

It's top secret, but you know, it was just
recently established.

Our superior, Lieutenant Colonel Carpenter,
created it to demonstrate the usefulness of magic.

Is it okay for you to tell me even though it's top
secret?

If the child can use magic, then there shouldn't
be a problem.

Most of the children here have similar
circumstances to yours.

Yeah... I don't come from a wealthy enough family
to afford attending the academy.

Alright, enough with the gloomy talk. Let me show
you around the dormitory.

Since I'm the oldest sister here, I'll teach you
various things.
Are you the leader? Is this unit going to be okay?

You're being cheeky. I have confidence in handling
magic, you know.

Just now, I defeated the monster that you couldn't
defeat with a single blow, didn't I?
Hehe, you can rely on me as your older sister.
